title: 30,000 Boeing workers strike
text:
YOUR BUSINESS AUTHORITY
Springfield, MO
More than 30,000 Boeing workers who are members of the International Association of Machinists and Aerospace Workers union have gone on strike.
The strike comes after union members voted 94.6% against a tentative labor contract with Boeing.
Workers in the Seattle area and in Oregon are involved in the strike.
Read more from
CNBC.
